posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 26', 'OR Text', '26', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath, approximately 1377 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'One Hundred Grand has thought through everything – so you don’t have to.', "Featuring open floor plans for 1- and 2- bedroom flats, and 3-bedroom townhomes, you'll have plenty of space to unwind and refresh.", 'Sleek modern kitchens and hardwood style flooring pamper you in style.', 'Not to mention balconies and plentiful open spaces.', 'Time to get outside?', 'Take a dip or a lap in our refreshing pool, or entertain your friends in our clubhouse featuring billiards and a demonstration kitchen.', 'Nestled between San Mateo and Redwood City, One Hundred Grand boasts a quick commute to all things Silicon Valley.', 'Make your move to One Hundred Grand.', 'Features:', "Wood-style Flooring, Ample Storage Throughout, 18'Ceilings*, Quartz Surface Countertops, Full-Size Capacity In-Home Washer/Dryer, Stainless Steel Appliance Suite, Private Patios & Balconies*, Modern Chef's Kitchen, Thoughtfully Designed Apartment Homes, Spectacular Views*", '*In Select Units', 'Community Amenities:', 'Pool & Spa, Pet Wash & Dog Run, EV Charging Stations, Outdoor Fireside Lounge & BBQ, Dry Cleaning Pick up/Drop Off, Business Center & WIFI, Weights & Cardio, Coffee Lounge, Shuttle to CalTrain, Bicycle Repair Studio, Billiards Room, Valet Trash Service, We Love Pets!, Yoga & TRX, Private Bike Lockers', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', '0NrjJbSIr97E']
